	<p>Disclaimer!<br><span id="disclaimer_content">This webapp & all related content are for demonstration purposes only.<br>This webapp is a clone of the popular webapp Bitly.<br>This app is not used for commercialization.<br>This webapp was developed by Joey Chan.</span></p>
</div>

<div id="footer_logo">
	<div id="main_logo">
		<a href="/"><img src="img/main_logo.png" /></a>
	</div>
</div>